{"tid":2258614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金門烈嶼守備大隊戰車連將汰除M41A3輕戰車並以M41D輕戰車取代","createTime":"2020-10-26T07:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T11:37:36.000Z","uid":292499,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b34b8e8426dcd6576ab6499c3d0009ba4e71ea6e","tid":2258614,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:30:54.000Z","msg":"陸軍烈嶼守備大隊M41A3戰車連將全面汰除裝備，由軍備局209廠檢整14至15輛妥善的M41D戰車，運赴前線接手防務。這項專案將針對本島的M41D戰車，以「拆零納補」方式，在不增加預算原則下進行檢整。據了解，M41D戰車雖然老舊，但妥善率高，且當年性能提升後，至今仍堪稱擁有陸軍最先進的瞄準與射控系統，可射擊翼穩定脫殼穿甲彈。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n國軍以本島車輛性能提升50輛M41D戰車，改裝柴油引擎、更換主砲與射控、加裝夜視系統，M41D是我國獨有的型號，目前本島堪用待檢整的車輛，都是裝騎連汰除的裝備。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4964089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F4964089&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=76874e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4964089</a>"},{"pid":"3d837d7babb0b71fd555f2d349ae77fdfc636919","tid":2258614,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb01ce078d7e6d00ef78d955acffd4be51d13334","tid":2258614,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6600c33fa17371030a094ed1ba280e0942d530c","tid":2258614,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa